        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does Nightwatch include a site audit?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes — a basic site audit is included on all paid plans. It is solid for technical hygiene (crawl errors, meta issues, broken links) but not as deep as Ahrefs Site Audit or Semrush. Most agencies use Nightwatch's audit for client reports and a heavier tool for diagnosis." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is Nightwatch worth it in 2026?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For agencies and in-house SEO teams: yes — at $39–$79/mo it is the best price-to-feature rank tracker in the category. For business owners without a content team: Nightwatch tracks rankings but won't produce content. theStacc handles the entire content engine for $99/mo." }},
