        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the best Nightwatch alternatives?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For rank tracking at scale: AccuRanker ($129/mo) or SE Ranking ($55/mo). For all-in-one SEO with rank tracking included: Ahrefs ($129/mo) or Semrush ($139/mo). For done-for-you content + GBP + tracking in one stack: theStacc ($99/mo)." }},
